These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
House: tower, farmhouse, cottage
1. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
2. the tower house is on the right of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| House   | farmhouse | cottage | tower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, july, may
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Birthday   | march | july | may |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod, modern
1. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
2. the modern house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| House   | gothic-revival | cape-cod | modern |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, ritmeester, bongani
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Cigar   | vegafina | bongani | ritmeester |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, soul, classical
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of classical is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | soul | jazz | classical |

 #################################

 
